    MIDAS Sound System 0.7 Beta 1

MIDAS is a 32-bit digital music and sound
system, for MS-DOS (Watcom C & DJGPP), 
Win32 (C and Delphi) and Linux. It plays 
Protracker, ST3 and FT2 modules, plus 
individual samples and digital audio 
streams. Full source code and pre-compiled 
libraries for all platforms are included.
  - CONTAINS SUBDIRECTORIES! -

 Note! This is a MS-DOS only release!
